# Prayer App – Project Overview

- **Frontend**: Angular 21, standalone components, Tailwind v4, Capacitor (iOS/Android).
- **Backend**: Supabase (auth, Postgres, Edge Functions). Edge Functions are Deno in `supabase/functions/`.
- **Testing**: Vitest + @testing-library/angular for unit tests; Playwright for e2e.
- **Key paths**: `src/app/` (components, pages, services, guards, types), `src/styles.css` (Tailwind + theme), `src/environments/` (env config), `supabase/functions/<name>/index.ts` (Edge Functions).
- **Notable deps**: @supabase/supabase-js, @sentry/angular, @capacitor/*, lucide-angular, @planningcenter/api-client.
- Prefer existing services (`SupabaseService`, `ToastService`, etc.) and shared types in `src/app/types/` when adding features.
- Before finishing work: **`npm run pre-handoff`**, **`ReadLints`** on touched files, logic review. See [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md), [verify-before-done.mdc](verify-before-done.mdc), [pre-handoff skill](skills/pre-handoff/SKILL.md).
